OL,3,CMan charged after 'threatening' emails
OL,4,Csent to girls schools
OL,6,FA man has been charged after
OL,7,F"threatening" hoax emails were sent to
OL,8,Fthree girls schools, causing some to
OL,9,Fgo into lockdown.
OL,11,FHolly Lodge Girl's College in West
OL,12,FDerby, Greenbank High School, in
OL,13,FSouthport, and The Belvidere Academy,
OL,14,Fin Liverpool, were all targeted within
OL,15,Fthe space of a week.
OL,17,FDarren Rigby, 21, from Runcorn, has
OL,18,Fbeen charged with three counts of
OL,19,Fsending communication threatening
OL,20,Fdeath or serious harm, which falls
OL,21,Funder the Online Safety Act.
